import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground } from 'docz'
import Stage from './../stage';
import { TilingSprite } from './../index'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"tilingsprite"}}>{`TilingSprite`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"props"}}>{`Props`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"http://pixijs.download/dev/docs/PIXI.extras.TilingSprite.html"}}>{`http://pixijs.download/dev/docs/PIXI.extras.TilingSprite.html`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"usage"}}>{`Usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<Stage width={500} height={300}>
  <TilingSprite
    image={\'https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/s.cdpn.io/693612/p2.jpeg\'}
    width={500}
    height={300}
    tilePosition={{ x: 100, y: 150 }}
    tileScale={{ x: 0.1, y: 2 }}
  />
</Stage>`} __scope={{props,Stage,TilingSprite}}>
  <Stage width={500} height={300}>
    <TilingSprite image={'https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/s.cdpn.io/693612/p2.jpeg'}
                  width={500} 
                  height={300} 
                  tilePosition={{ x: 100, y: 150 }}
                  tileScale={{ x: 0.1, y: 2 }} />
  </Stage>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"example"}}>{`Example`}</MDXTag>
<iframe 
  height={500} 
  scrolling="no"
  title="Container" 
  src="//codepen.io/inlet/embed/a6b5965c309e78fd1306a99c22b38d79/?height=300&theme-id=33987&default-tab=result&embed-version=2"
  frameBorder="no" 
  allowtransparency="true"
  allowFullScreen="true"
  style={{ width: '100%' }} /></MDXTag>
